"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-no-one-prayed-over-their-graves-by-khaled-khalifa-72bd9b4?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">葬礼之后和其他故事</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          wrap
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-no-one-prayed-over-their-graves-by-khaled-khalifa-72bd9b4"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-823322?width=639&amp;height=945" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">诺普F</span></div></div></div><p><strong>作者：泰莎·哈德利</strong><em>克诺夫</em></p><p>“强烈的洞察力和认知”时刻激发了这位形式大师的十几个新故事。萨克斯评论。</p><p> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-no-one-prayed-over-their-graves-by-khaled-khalifa-72bd9b4?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/brothers-and-sisters-review-the-age-of-the-allmans-956e44a4?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">兄弟姐妹：奥尔曼兄弟乐队和定义 70 年代专辑的内幕故事</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          wrap
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/brothers-and-sisters-review-the-age-of-the-allmans-956e44a4"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-823323?width=639&amp;height=971" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">圣马丁学院</span></div></div></div><p><strong>作者：艾伦·保罗</strong>|<em>圣马丁</em></p><p>即使在失去了两名创始成员之后，这支来自佐治亚州的乐队仍然创造了一种吸引观众的乡村布鲁斯音乐。加文·爱德华兹评论。</p><p> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/brothers-and-sisters-review-the-age-of-the-allmans-956e44a4?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/completely-mad-review-across-the-ocean-with-an-oar-5afb65c0?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">完全疯狂：汤姆·麦克莱恩、约翰·费尔法克斯和史诗般的单人划船横渡大西洋的比赛</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          wrap
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/completely-mad-review-across-the-ocean-with-an-oar-5afb65c0"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-823324?width=639&amp;height=947" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
